Ryno, Sarge and Doctor K: A look back at Mets-Cubs in '84 FILE - In this Sept. 14, 1984 file photo, Kevin Kellogg, left front, joins in a cheer with a crowd of fans waiting to get into the bleachers before a baseball game between the Chicago Cubs and the New York Mets game in Chicago. At right is Jerry Pritikin and his nephew Barry Manhoin. The Mets and Cubs, who are playing each other in Game 3 of the NL Championship Series on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, had a memorable race for the NL East title in 1984.
